Some of the challenges include high initial costs, concerns about data privacy, and the need for standardization of biometric technologies in the automotive industry.

6. What are the different types of biometric access systems used in the automotive industry?
Common types of biometric access systems include fingerprint recognition, facial recognition, iris recognition, and voice recognition.

